Package: RIFT
Title: Rare variant Influential Filtering Tool
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Rachel", "Blumhagen", email = "rachel.blumhagen@cuanschutz.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package includes software for running the rare variant influential filtering tool (RIFT).  RIFT leverages the influence of the variant on the aggregate test of association by quantifying the change in the aggregate test when that variant is removed.  This version is limited to the aggregate test of SKAT-O.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
  SKAT,
  dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
